## Technical Architecture for Goals UI Enhancement

### Overview
This epic enhances the Goals feature with three main capabilities:
1. **Edit Goal Functionality**: Full CRUD support for goals
2. **Animated Progress Charts**: Visual progress tracking using fl_chart
3. **Realtime Progress Updates**: Live UI updates with animations

### Architecture Patterns (EXISTING - MUST FOLLOW)

#### BLoC Pattern (from create_goal_bloc.dart)
```dart
// Events: Use sealed classes with Equatable
sealed class EditGoalEvent extends Equatable {
  const EditGoalEvent();
}

final class EditGoalLoadRequested extends EditGoalEvent {
  const EditGoalLoadRequested({required this.goalId});
  final String goalId;
  @override
  List<Object?> get props => [goalId];
}

// States: Use sealed classes with Equatable
sealed class EditGoalState extends Equatable {
  const EditGoalState();
}

final class EditGoalLoaded extends EditGoalState {
  const EditGoalLoaded({required this.goal});
  final GroupGoal goal;
  @override
  List<Object?> get props => [goal];
}

// BLoC: Inject use cases, handle events with on<Event>
class EditGoalBloc extends Bloc<EditGoalEvent, EditGoalState> {
  EditGoalBloc({required UpdateGoalUseCase updateGoalUseCase})
      : _updateGoalUseCase = updateGoalUseCase,
        super(const EditGoalInitial()) {
    on<EditGoalLoadRequested>(_onLoadRequested);
    on<EditGoalSubmitted>(_onSubmitted);
  }
}
```

#### Use Case Pattern (from create_goal_usecase.dart)
```dart
class UpdateGoalUseCase {
  UpdateGoalUseCase({required GoalsRepository repository})
      : _repository = repository;
  final GoalsRepository _repository;

  Future<GroupGoal> call({
    required String goalId,
    String? name,
    String? description,
    int? targetSteps,
    DateTime? startDate,
    DateTime? endDate,
  }) async {
    return _repository.updateGoal(
      goalId: goalId,
      name: name,
      description: description,
      targetSteps: targetSteps,
      startDate: startDate,
      endDate: endDate,
    );
  }
}
```

#### fl_chart Pattern (from weekly_chart.dart)
```dart
class AnimatedProgressChart extends StatelessWidget {
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return LineChart(
      LineChartData(
        lineBarsData: [
          LineChartBarData(
            spots: _buildSpots(),
            isCurved: true,
            curveSmoothness: 0.3,
            belowBarData: BarAreaData(
              show: true,
              gradient: LinearGradient(...),
            ),
          ),
        ],
        lineTouchData: LineTouchData(
          touchTooltipData: LineTouchTooltipData(...),
        ),
      ),
    );
  }
}
```

#### Router Pattern (from app_router.dart)
```dart
GoRoute(
  path: RouteNames.editGoal,
  name: 'editGoal',
  builder: (context, state) {
    final goalId = state.uri.queryParameters['goalId'] ?? '';
    return BlocProvider(
      create: (_) => sl<EditGoalBloc>()
        ..add(EditGoalLoadRequested(goalId: goalId)),
      child: EditGoalPage(goalId: goalId),
    );
  },
),
```

### Dependency Injection (from injection_container.dart)
```dart
// Register use case
sl.registerLazySingleton<UpdateGoalUseCase>(
  () => UpdateGoalUseCase(repository: sl<GoalsRepository>()),
);

// Register bloc as factory (new instance per use)
sl.registerFactory<EditGoalBloc>(
  () => EditGoalBloc(
    updateGoalUseCase: sl<UpdateGoalUseCase>(),
    getGoalDetailsUseCase: sl<GetGoalDetailsUseCase>(),
  ),
);
```

